#: applications/luci-app-ddns/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/ddns/overview.js:361
msgid ""
"BusyBox's nslookup and hostip do not support TCP instead of the default UDP "
"when sending requests to the DNS server!"
msgstr ""
"nslookup ແລະ hostip ຂອງ BusyBox ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບການໃຊ້ TCP ແທນ UDP ຕາມຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ເວລາສົ່ງຄຳຮ້ອ"
"ງຂໍໄປຍັງເຊີບເວີ DNS!"

